title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 23 2022

description:
Chicago Mayor Lightfoot complains about SCOTUS gun ruling. GOP Senate sellouts side with Dems on gun control bill. The Sexton Plan to fight crime: Stop letting criminals go. New York criminal arrested and let go 122 times. Hochul's dumb argument: They only had muskets when they wrote the Constitution. Quinnipiac Poll spells doom for the Biden Regime. MSNBC Biden apologist: Quit complaining, America! Biden blames Ukraine war for faltering economy. Alabama Senator Tommy Tuberville joins us on the 50th Anniversary of Title IX, which is under attack by Biden, codifying transgender participation in sports as a civil right.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
